org.apache.flex.compiler.tree.as

Interface IIterationFlowNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IASNode, ISourceLocation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    IterationFlowNode

    public interface IIterationFlowNode
extends IASNode
    An AST node representing a break, continue, or goto statement.

    The shape of this node is: 

     IIterationFlowNode 
   IIdentifierNode <-- getLabelNode()
    For example, 
    continue label1;
    is represented as 
     IIterationFlowNode "continue"
   IIdentifierNode "label1"
    If there is no label, the child node is not present.
